original: Enwall, Gustav Adlolif Heilmer, kyrkoherde, Barlingibo, f. 1/8/08 i Visby. — Stud:ex. i Sthlm 27, teol. fil. ex. 30, teol. kand. samt prakt. teol. prov 33’, prästv. f. Visby stift 34. V. pastor i Stenkumla 34, pastorsadj. i När s. å., kyrkoh. i Barlingbo, Ekeby, Endre o. Hejdeby sed. 40. Ordf. i Barlingbo, Endre o. Hejdeby kyrko-iStämmor o. past :kyrkostämma, i Bar-linigbo O’. Hejdeby ’skolråd.
translated: Enwall, Gustav Adolf Heilmer, clergyman, born on August 1, 1908 in Visby. He passed his studentexamen in Stockholm in 1927, theological degree exam in 1930 and theological candidate and practical theology exam in 1933. He was ordained as a priest in Visby diocese in 1934. He served as an assistant pastor in Stenkumla in 1934, pastors assistant in När the same year, and later became the vicar in Barlingbo, Ekeby, Endre and Hejdeby from 1940. He was also the chairman of the church meetings and pastors' church meeting in Barlingbo, Endre and Hejdeby, and the school council in Barlingbo and Hejdeby. He got married in 19__.
